Revision history for Perl extension Cvs::Trigger

0.04  2009/03/22
    (ms) Skip tests on platforms which don't have cvs installed.

0.03  2008/03/25
    (ms) removed init() from Cvs::Temp new()
    (ms) fixed problem with messages containing a single quote
    (ms) compatible with cvs 1.12.* (needs rebuilding admin CVSROOT)

0.02  2008/02/10
    (ms) test suite fixes to cope with File::Path changes

0.01  2006/04/06
    (ms) Where it all began.
